ðŸ“ˆ Dashboard Features
Total Price by Store:
Displays the sum of product prices for each store to show overall affordability.

Best Store for Each Product:
Compares prices per product across stores to identify the cheapest option.

Color-coded visualizations for easy comparison and interpretation.

ðŸ§  Key Insights
Walmart has the highest total price, while Costco shows a lower overall cost.

The best store varies by product, meaning shoppers can save more by buying strategically rather than sticking to one store.

Visual comparison makes price differences immediately clear for decision-making.

